Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.22,0:00:18.15,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算翻過所有的雜誌也沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.51,0:00:22.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在這搖頭嘆息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.39,0:00:26.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本找不到 與我相稱的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.63,0:00:30.54,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世紀末的流行色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.86,0:00:34.58,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都無法 討得你的歡心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.78,0:00:38.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉讓你失望了 說笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.54,0:00:43.17,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰這樣不穩的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.71,0:00:47.34,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖晃晃的又有什麼不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.50,0:00:51.35,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此還是得向前邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.74,0:00:56.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說  一點也不成問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.97,0:01:05.07,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是與我緊緊地纏繞的話不行喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你  別用那種冷冷的眼神望著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.06,0:01:12.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我照著自己的步調去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.07,0:01:16.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話我很快就會崩潰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:20.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰這樣不穩的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.88,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖晃晃的又有什麼不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.33,0:01:29.41,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此還是得向前邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.72,0:01:34.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說  一點也不成問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.84,0:21:47.82,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  真正的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.35,0:21:53.52,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  這就是愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.72,0:21:58.89,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰冷的黑暗中  伸手尋找溫暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.02,0:22:04.78,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天  奇蹟也一定會發生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.31,0:22:07.36,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&Hdc\3a&Hdc\4a&Hdc}Free Magic 如果有愛 就絕對有具體的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.36,0:22:17.73,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 如果有愛 就絕對有具體的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.25,0:22:28.72,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 現在 在我手中 有誕生的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.96,0:22:36.97,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是精神飽滿  也不能   太過勉強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.35,0:22:42.32,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  把些微的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.76,0:22:53.43,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  凝聚起來  培育茁壯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.03,0:00:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞬間明白所有真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.03,0:00:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要開始就不會停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.82,0:00:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是傳說的解決篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.56,0:00:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詭計和證據都是意料之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.70,0:00:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.29,0:00:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.27,0:00:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.41,0:00:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.19,0:01:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們因為旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.48,0:01:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到一個有五重塔的幻塊寺參觀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.30,0:01:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是寺廟與開發公司有些紛爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.17,0:01:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後隔天早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.45,0:01:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開發公司的社長 小田英明先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.20,0:01:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現吊死在五重塔的塔頂前端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.04,0:01:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.04,0:01:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五重塔的傳說一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.10,0:02:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.43,0:02:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.80,0:02:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的第一現場就是這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.91,0:02:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的假設是正確的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.00,0:02:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生不是自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.86,0:02:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.29,0:02:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人大概就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.93,0:02:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候講了那句話的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.81,0:02:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.48,0:02:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的五重塔傳說(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.02,0:02:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在這裏做什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.20,0:02:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 掉在這裏的領帶夾不是小田先生的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.63,0:02:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.86,0:02:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.51,0:02:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是小田先生的領帶夾嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.57,0:02:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.90,0:02:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面鑲著鑽石的領帶夾並不是常有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.84,0:03:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾村先生 我想你來確認一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.72,0:03:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是社長的領帶夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.88,0:03:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 還敢說我們偷東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.34,0:03:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想錢包也掉在那附近吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.45,0:03:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如查清楚一點再下結論吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.07,0:03:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣小田先生並沒有遇到強盜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.08,0:03:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是在自殺的時候不小心讓領帶夾掉在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.44,0:03:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.95,0:03:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏距離五重塔有幾十公尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.54,0:03:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是自殺的時候掉下來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.83,0:03:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得距離太遠了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.04,0:03:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是這樣掉下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.87,0:03:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生懊惱著該不該在這裏自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.43,0:03:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就在那時候不小心掉下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.51,0:03:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是領帶夾不是那麼容易就可以掉落的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.52,0:03:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.26,0:03:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生的手肘那裏有草跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.06,0:03:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.67,0:04:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領帶夾不是掉在這裏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.86,0:04:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.78,0:04:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些草跡是在這裏沾到的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.23,0:04:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.16,0:04:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生果然是在這裏和某人起紛爭而倒下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.57,0:04:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要把小田先生的屍體放下來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.99,0:04:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繩子好像不夠長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.39,0:04:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小田先生的腳無法站在欄杆上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.60,0:04:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.57,0:04:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小田先生放下來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.09,0:04:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的腳站不到欄杆嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.42,0:04:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多相差五十公分左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.76,0:04:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.51,0:04:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不站在欄杆上面拉住繩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.01,0:04:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼自殺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.98,0:04:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 這點你怎麼解釋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.64,0:04:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.36,0:04:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不成問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.09,0:04:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.96,0:04:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生在懊惱著要不要自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.37,0:04:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後爬到五重塔上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.53,0:04:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算少了五十公分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.59,0:04:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種地步不想死也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.43,0:04:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.43,0:05:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是跳上去吊頸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.40,0:05:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有很多狀況證明是他殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.22,0:05:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 就算是他殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.62,0:05:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這就必須有人背著失去意識的小田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.41,0:05:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過那些狹窄的通道到頂樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.55,0:05:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過在五重塔上面和小田先生身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.27,0:05:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有這些跡象出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.07,0:05:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要如何將小田先生吊在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.22,0:05:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個短了五十公分的圈圈裏面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.44,0:05:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.67,0:05:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣越是證明他殺的可能性越低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.94,0:05:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.06,0:05:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生如果不是自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.80,0:05:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本無法吊在五重塔塔頂的前端的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.38,0:05:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你們已經有了結論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.98,0:06:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要用人為的力量去改變天罰再等一百年吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.73,0:06:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點夾著尾巴滾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.34,0:06:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的確有幾個疑問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.37,0:06:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過卻沒有可以推翻他是自殺的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.25,0:06:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過小田先生的確是被人殺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.15,0:06:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是如何將小田先生吊在五重塔的前端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.91,0:06:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果無法解開這個謎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.24,0:06:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個案件就會被當作自殺來處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.42,0:06:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊是綁在欄杆上面的繩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.77,0:06:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會是活結呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.60,0:06:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.64,0:06:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.66,0:06:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個謎底終於解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.01,0:06:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用這個方法的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.34,0:06:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以把繩子綁在欄杆上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.17,0:06:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 不可以亂碰那些東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.46,0:06:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的推理沒有錯誤的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西應該還在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.32,0:07:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.03,0:07:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想犯人一定是用這個方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.25,0:07:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓小田先生變成自殺的樣子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.57,0:07:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面還有新的摩擦過的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.57,0:07:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報應啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.53,0:07:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然假借傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.13,0:07:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這種詭計殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.54,0:07:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只剩下證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.30,0:07:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找出那個人做的證據才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.47,0:08:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是一個另類自殺 不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.86,0:08:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在總算破案了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.46,0:08:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我卻覺得這個案子好像有什麼疑點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.63,0:08:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還這樣子講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.80,0:08:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就在報告書上面寫說是因為報應而死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.52,0:08:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.49,0:08:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣寫的話 我會被革職的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.15,0:08:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.12,0:08:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以回酒店去了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.76,0:08:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那些員工一定很心急了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.32,0:08:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對 好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.79,0:08:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 請先留下聯絡地址和電話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.87,0:08:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在酒店裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.51,0:08:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 這麼多錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.47,0:08:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.60,0:08:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.86,0:08:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事請聯絡這裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.94,0:08:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾村先生好像帶了不少錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.54,0:08:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那該不會是小田先生的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.59,0:08:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.20,0:09:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和社長的錢包形狀和顏色完全不一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.96,0:09:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是今天要發給員工的薪水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.29,0:09:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的 我是開玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.12,0:09:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要嚇我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.55,0:09:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然小田已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.00,0:09:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼主題公園的計畫應該就無效了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.39,0:09:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在不馬上中止的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.71,0:09:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司就會倒閉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.52,0:09:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這座寺廟的所有權應該也可以歸還了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.07,0:09:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.85,0:09:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份所有權社長已經交給我來保管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.40,0:09:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想現在還給你們應該是最好的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.06,0:09:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 淡海大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.47,0:09:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾村先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.99,0:09:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.34,0:09:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我看錯你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.66,0:09:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.59,0:09:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這份所有權也是一個誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.06,0:09:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就再替小田念個經吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.02,0:10:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當他最後做了一件好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.36,0:10:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我也可以放心回到總寺院繼續修行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.19,0:10:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在出發的話…傍晚就可以到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.87,0:10:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去整理一下五重塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.73,0:10:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.38,0:10:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能不承認的…那決定性的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.27,0:10:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人果然是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.62,0:10:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.26,0:10:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫溝警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.98,0:10:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.87,0:10:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.32,0:10:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個事件一定是自殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.76,0:10:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果毛利先生這樣講的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.67,0:10:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一早就被人給吵醒 害我現在好想睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.60,0:10:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回酒店再睡一覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.66,0:11:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 睡蟲突然出現…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.48,0:11:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將鈕釦型擴音器放在大叔的額頭上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.36,0:11:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這是個自殺案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以結案了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.30,0:11:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.98,0:11:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫溝警官 真是拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.81,0:11:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.86,0:11:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才已經出現不少提示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.20,0:11:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼還是不明白呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.98,0:11:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.61,0:11:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是他殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.51,0:11:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果真是這樣子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.67,0:11:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你現在才講呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.14,0:11:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我認為你應該可以自己發現到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.73,0:11:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.53,0:11:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我太遲鈍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.46,0:11:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.92,0:12:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就讓我表演一個推理秀給大家看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.51,0:12:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那裏 橫溝警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.70,0:12:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在想做一個實驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.79,0:12:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以請那些警官幫個忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.43,0:12:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.51,0:12:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們馬上去做準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.23,0:12:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先將一個和小田先生重量相當的袋子放在草地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.53,0:12:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袋口用繩子綁住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.78,0:12:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那條繩子繞到五重塔的五樓屋頂的前端上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.49,0:12:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後通過欄杆再延伸到地面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.21,0:12:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綁到現在已經不用的水井上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.21,0:12:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再將繩子綁在那些鋼鐵上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.13,0:12:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓在一條很容易掉下去的鐵棒上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.89,0:12:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.62,0:12:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 橫溝警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.62,0:12:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用力拉一下那條繩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吊…吊上去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.94,0:13:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小田先生一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.70,0:13:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.56,0:13:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是這次報應的真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.25,0:13:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繩子上面燒焦的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.31,0:13:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為掛在屋頂前端上經過強力的摩擦而成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.59,0:13:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是一條新的繩子摩擦過後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.05,0:13:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會出現這種現象的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.15,0:13:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而領帶夾掉落的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.14,0:13:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能就是犯罪的第一現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.22,0:13:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是犯人是如何將繩子套到小田先生的頸部的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生也會做抵抗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.44,0:13:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並沒有發現他被毆打過的痕跡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.65,0:13:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 這是最大的疑點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.44,0:14:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我重新說明一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.30,0:14:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先犯人利用手機將小田先生叫出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.13,0:14:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再找機會將繩子套到小田先生的頸部的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.24,0:14:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時拉動繩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.86,0:14:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓鋼鐵掉到井裏面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.23,0:14:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.81,0:14:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生在被繩子拉上去之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.07,0:14:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一點時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.73,0:14:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以將繩子從頸部上拿開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.93,0:14:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以犯人就用腳絆倒小田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.70,0:14:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.34,0:14:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是像小田先生這樣的人也很容易在不注意中被絆倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.72,0:14:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小田先生手肘上的草跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.50,0:14:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在這個時候沾到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.11,0:14:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領帶夾也是在這個時候掉下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.64,0:14:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後小田先生在還沒解開繩子之前就已經被拉上去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.89,0:14:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生的確是倒下了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.48,0:14:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.86,0:15:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳跟的地方就不會有泥巴的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.96,0:15:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.78,0:15:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.29,0:15:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.08,0:15:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成這個事件是很多人一起做的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.09,0:15:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你終於發現這個問題了 橫溝警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.91,0:15:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為小田先生是個一百公斤巨型身材的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.44,0:15:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果犯人獨自一個人想把繩子綁在欄杆上面的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.62,0:15:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本無法拉動繩子 所以只能握住繩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.91,0:15:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在切斷繩子的同時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.68,0:15:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繩子就會被拉過去 從手中滑落啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.56,0:15:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.34,0:15:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨自一個人的話怎麼可能把繩子綁到欄杆上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.69,0:15:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.74,0:15:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨自一個人犯案的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.11,0:15:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.17,0:15:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼做到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.06,0:15:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人在通過欄杆的那條繩子上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.49,0:15:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打了一個活結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.42,0:15:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.09,0:16:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在繩子中間打了個圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.32,0:16:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經叫五重塔上面的警官這樣做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.19,0:16:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫他們試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.40,0:16:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把繩子切斷綁在欄杆上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.34,0:16:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.94,0:16:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先將活結繞到欄杆上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.89,0:16:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後拿棒子穿過那個圈圈成為一個定點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.70,0:16:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把外面的繩子給割斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.58,0:16:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將割斷的繩子穿過圈圈再綁起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.63,0:16:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把棒子抽掉就完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫溝警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經把繩子綁在欄杆上面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.98,0:16:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨自一個人就可以做到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.75,0:16:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就是把割斷的繩子給拉回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.30,0:16:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丟到古井裏面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.33,0:16:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣利用傳說而設計出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.96,0:16:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓小田先生看起來像自殺的計畫就完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想犯人唯一的失誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.35,0:17:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是讓小田先生的腳差五十公分才能站在欄杆上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.30,0:17:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這點我才會懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.28,0:17:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生並不是自殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.33,0:17:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠做到這種事情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.94,0:17:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了寺廟的人之外…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.46,0:17:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.90,0:17:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你的意思是說犯人就是我們其中一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.33,0:17:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.38,0:17:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用詭計殺害小田先生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.67,0:17:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾村先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.23,0:17:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.43,0:17:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在胡說什麼啊 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.29,0:17:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對這間寺廟一點都不清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.54,0:17:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是ODA酒店的經理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.67,0:17:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是ODA觀光的高級職員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.60,0:17:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假裝說為了要建造主題公園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.11,0:17:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可以拿到寺廟的藍圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.87,0:17:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以很輕易地知道五重塔的高度和古井的距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.07,0:17:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要工人將鋼鐵放在古井附近的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.39,0:18:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.41,0:18:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這次的殺人計畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.17,0:18:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的…的確是我叫人這麼做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.41,0:18:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就算是我叫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.89,0:18:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是工作上需要用到的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.14,0:18:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且毛利先生也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.25,0:18:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我出差去了 根本不在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.67,0:18:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.76,0:18:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會知道小田先生和春海先生昨晚的爭吵呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.83,0:18:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來到這裏的時候這樣子講過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.09,0:18:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過因為知道昨天的爭吵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.77,0:18:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方要用法律方式來解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.75,0:18:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以非常擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.20,0:18:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春海先生是昨晚才回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.52,0:18:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好和你錯過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.50,0:18:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你為什麼會知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.87,0:18:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…社長告訴我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.53,0:18:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我在東京的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.26,0:18:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長打手機給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.42,0:18:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.92,0:18:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確實是在手機裏面聽到這件事情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.38,0:19:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是在為了殺害小田先生而把他叫來這裏的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.54,0:19:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再鬧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.88,0:19:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你說我是犯人 證據拿出來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.19,0:19:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨晚還在這裏的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.46,0:19:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據就在你身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.36,0:19:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個決定性的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.13,0:19:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的嗎 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.35,0:19:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去看看尾村先生的錢包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.54,0:19:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以拿出來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.31,0:19:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是說錢上面有社長的指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.18,0:19:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是社長給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.48,0:19:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不能證明什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.73,0:19:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 證據在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.46,0:19:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就在紙幣裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.02,0:19:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一張收據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.03,0:19:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.60,0:19:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是ODA酒店的收據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.18,0:19:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九月十二日 十九點四十分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.42,0:19:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是購買雪茄的收據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.54,0:19:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.28,0:19:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是昨晚我們和小田先生一起吃飯的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.79,0:20:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生收下的收據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.71,0:20:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在那之前就離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.46,0:20:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後沒有再見過小田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.94,0:20:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生的收據會在你的錢包裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.66,0:20:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.26,0:20:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你殺害小田先生之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.19,0:20:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現錢包掉在草地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.87,0:20:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以決定順手牽羊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.81,0:20:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有發覺紙幣裏面夾著一張收據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.14,0:20:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果調查一下那張收據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.04,0:20:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面應該也有小田先生的指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.68,0:20:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底如何 尾村先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.48,0:20:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不承認嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.66,0:20:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到這種事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.61,0:20:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種事之下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.63,0:20:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被揭穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.18,0:20:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的動機到底是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.93,0:20:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了逃稅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.51,0:20:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司的經營開始走下坡路的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.27,0:21:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長要我做逃稅的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.73,0:21:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個 我也收到不少好處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這是社長為了預防被發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.04,0:21:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候要我背上所有的責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.62,0:21:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會給了我這麼多的好處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.39,0:21:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才對小田先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.00,0:21:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想趁著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.37,0:21:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我替公司做了這麼多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.79,0:21:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來卻像蜥蜴一樣尾巴被切掉之前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.17,0:23:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易有一個旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.71,0:23:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只要和爸爸在一起都會有事件出現呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.30,0:23:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.23,0:23:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是爸爸被詛咒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.39,0:23:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好來廟裏玩 趁機將那厄運給趕走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.67,0:23:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混…混帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.42,0:23:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個偵探啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.06,0:23:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探當然要有事件發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.93,0:23:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是糧食的來源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.78,0:23:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外就是我的生意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.69,0:23:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做名偵探的就是不斷會有事件來挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.13,0:23:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.44,0:23:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔的確是個多意外的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.83,0:23:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.75,0:24:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是新一的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.53,0:24:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.87,0:24:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工藤新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.93,0:24:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.92,0:24:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Special
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.70,0:24:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中的密室  工藤新一首次的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.97,0:24:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.70,0:24:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暈車藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.65,0:24:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次是特別篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.56,0:24:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個小時的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.62,0:24:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒登場的傢伙 喝～
